'From Squeak3.3alpha of 30 January 2002 [latest update: #4689] on 30 January 2002 at 11:17:26 am'!"Change Set:		ModuleBrowseProtocolFix-nkDate:			30 January 2002Author:			Ned KonzThis fixes the 'browse protocol' on class-side definitions in change set browsers. This bug was introduced in the Modules code, so this change set should only be applied to 4689 or later images.It probably fixes some other things."!!Object methodsFor: 'viewer' stamp: 'nk 1/30/2002 11:12'!uniqueNameForReferenceOrNil	"If the receiver has a unique name for reference, return it here, else return nil"	| aName |	(References definedNames includesIdentity: self) ifTrue: [^ References definedNames keyAtValue: self].	(aName _ Smalltalk keyAtValue: self ifAbsent: [nil]) ifNotNil: [^ aName].	^ nil! !